	* Fix: sessiond: fix possible buffer overflow warning
	* Fix: tests: app unregistering is not guaranteed by app lifetime
	* Fix: lttng-ctl: tracing_group memory leaks
	* Fix: use <unistd.h> instead of <sys/unistd.h>
